text: But how do we use AI to actually build AI to put generative thinking, living, breathing applications into people's hands, and so it's not only new for developers, but it's new for the business owners, it's new when you're thinking about companies being disrupted, it's new for the venture community, it's new for everyone, and so how do we democratize and actually have this new technology to be disseminated to anyone who wants it, because now you know we have customers who are doing these amazing things and now can enable even more amazing things for their customers, so we have a mom and and daughter team who is you know building financial literacy or we have a CPG brand who takes ocean plastic and turns that into activeware right like so not just the super technical large enterprise companies, but like everyone across the spectrum.
